<plot>Joe McDoakes (George O'Hanlon) asks for a raise and is informed by his boss that the employee selected by him to run the office while he is on vacation will get a raise. Joe works hard and is selected, but manages to get himself unselected when he hears his boss rehearsing for a gangster role in a play and Joe calls the police.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503840</url></doc>
